To further investigate the concentration influence of QDs in the monochromic QD-based silicone thin films, the time-resolved PL (TRPL) spectra of the thin films with different concentrations are measured and the decay curves are depicted in Fig. 3. It is known that PL decay curves can be expressed with a multi-exponential function, as illustrated by Eq. 1 [30],
