TRPL decay curves of R-QD (a) and O-QD (b)-based thin films. Lifetimes of R-QD (c) and O-QD (d)-based silicone gel thin films with different concentrations

The fitting parameters Ai and τi are listed in Table S1 and S2. The amplitude-weighted lifetimes of the R-QDs and O-QDs are selected as their lifetimes (τave) for further investigation. The lifetime can be calculated from the following Eq. 2 [31] and is listed in Table S1 and S2.
